tafsir[3]{c,v,t}:
  23,105,"It will be said to rebuke them: “Were the verses of the Qur’ān not recited to you in the world but you used to deny them?”"
  23,108,"Allah will say: “Sit in the fire and stay in there disgraced; never speak to me."
  23,112,"He will say: “How many years did you spend on earth? And how much time did you waste therein?”"